宴》的阿比盖尔·莫里斯（左）和凯莉·克拉克森（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/KellyClarkson-covers-The-Last-Dinner-Party-Nothing-Matters-Kellyoke-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯莉·克拉克森</a>翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴</a>》的歌曲“Nothing Matters”——您可以观看下面的视频。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">封面上的最后晚宴：巴洛克流行音乐的新加冕君主</a></strong></li></ul><p>作为“Kellyoke”部分的一部分，这位流行艺术家和她的乐队在<em>凯莉·克拉克森秀 (The Kelly Clarkson Show)</em>上现场表演了伦敦乐队 2023 年的突破单曲。</p><p>克拉克森仍然忠于原曲，但她确实在明确的副歌中加入了PG旋转。 “<em>你可以抱着我，就像他抱着她一样/我会爱你，就像什么都不重要一样</em>，”她唱道。</p><p>最后的晚宴派对后来在 YouTube 评论部分表达了他们的认可，并分享了一系列表情符号，其中包括一个白心符号。他们还在 Instagram 故事上发布了封面剪辑。</p><p>在这里查看凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 的《Nothing Matters》封面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 在《最后的晚宴》中翻唱《Nothing Matters》凯利奥克" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3MdR5fKpwNI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 2 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sophie-ellis-bextors-sensual-cover-of-the-last-dinner-partys-nothing-matters-3590157">Sophie Ellis-Bextor 在 BBC Radio 1 的 Live Lounge 露面时演奏了这首歌的现场版本</a>。</p><p>在“Kellyoke”系列中，克拉克森之前曾演绎过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-perform-say-it-aint-so-with-weezer-3757532">Weezer</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-u2s-mysterious-ways-3578341">U2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-the-arctic-monkeys-do-i-wanna-know-on-kellyoke-3390045">Arctic Monkeys</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-put-her-kellyoke-spin-on-the-smiths-how-soon-is-now-3221944">The Smiths</a>等乐队的经典曲目。今年年初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-and-kelsey-grammer-perform-the-frasier-theme-song-3568266">她与凯尔西·格拉默合作演绎了<em>《欢乐一家亲》</em>主题曲</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-have-begun-work-on-their-second-album-it-feels-like-were-doing-something-new-nme-radar-3771634">最后的晚餐派对最近透露他们已经开始制作第二张录音室专辑</a>。</p><p>他们的首张唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">“Prelude To Ecstasy”</a> （其中包含“Nothing Matters”）于二月发行。随后它<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-score-biggest-number-one-debut-album-in-nine-years-3585175">成为九年来英国销量第一的首张专辑</a>。上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-debut-albums-of-2024-so-far-radar-3768653"><em>NME</em>将这张唱片列为 2024 年迄今为止 10 首最佳首张专辑之一</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="关于对圣文森特的爱的最后晚宴和新材料计划|英国人 2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0n69ziYlFiI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 3 月，The Last Evening Party 接受 NME 采访，谈论新材料以及他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2024 年全英音乐节上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-on-the-response-to-debut-album-and-st-vincent-inspiration-3596430"><em>的</em>首张专辑的反响</a>——<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">在获得新星奖</a>前不久。</p><p>最后的晚宴派对在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>的另一个舞台上表演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-the-last-dinner-party-showcase-new-songs-at-other-stage-3770145">他们演奏了两首未发行的歌曲：“Second Best”和“The Killer”</a> 。</p><p>该乐队将于今年秋天开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-autumn-2024-european-tour-3755882">欧洲</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-add-three-shows-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3584408">英国/爱尔兰的巡回演出</a>，并将于下个月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-full-stage-times-line-up-3765102#:~:text=The%202024%20edition%20of%20Reading,into%20the%20current%20media%20landscape.">雷丁和利兹</a>演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-last-dinner-party-tickets/artist/5395177?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkC22SzPcSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找任何剩余门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-kelly-clarkson-covering-the-last-dinner-partys-nothing-matters-3776455">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 报道《最后的晚宴派对》(The Last Evening Party) 的《Nothing Matters》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
